<footer>
  <div class="footer-columns">
     <div class="footer-column">
      <h3 class="overskrift">FAQ</h3>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">What payment methods do we offer?</h4>
            <img class="arrow" src="/arrow.svg" alt="pil ned" />
          </div>
          <p class="answer">We offer: VISA - Mastercard - MobilePay - Cash</p>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">How do I book an appointment?</h4>
            <img class="arrow" src="/arrow.svg" alt="pil ned" />
          </div>
          <p class="answer">
            You can book an appointment by visiting the store, by insta, by the
            site or by calling the number: <br /><br /> + 45 60 18 16 63
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">How much does a tattoo cost?</h4>
            <img class="arrow" src="/arrow.svg" alt="pil ned" />
          </div>
          <p class="answer">
            The price depends on the size. We have a starting fee of DKK 800.
            Contact us for more information.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">
              Terms regarding advance payment & cancellation
