            5 days before the appointment.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">Preparation for tattoo session</h4>
            <img class="arrow" src="/arrow.svg" alt="pil ned" />
          </div>
          <p class="answer">
            We encourage you to avoird alcohol the days before and after your
            session for the best healing process. In addition, get a good meal
            before you show up.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item linebottom">
          <div class="q_arrow">
            <h4 class="question">How do I take care of my new tattoo?</h4>
            <img class="arrow" src="/arrow.svg" alt="pil ned" />
          </div>
          <p class="answer">
            You will receive an introduktion to how to treat your new tattoo
            after your session. <br /><br /> In case you have any questions, you
            can read more here: <a
              class="link_aftercare"
              href="https://mst.dk/borger/sundhed-og-kemi/personlig-pleje/think-before-you-ink/efter-tatovering"
              target="_blank">After care</a
            >
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-column">
      <div class="logo_bottom">
        <a href="/"><img src="/logo_tut_guld.svg" alt="logo" /></a>
      </div>
